<subSubSection pageId="179" pageNumber="782" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="179.[170,1375,722,1149]" pageId="179" pageNumber="782">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[171,521,1002,1031]" pageId="179" pageNumber="782">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List because this species is adapted to a single habitat (broadleaf forest), which is under threat.
</paragraph>
